text: Valery Martyshev (born 14 March 1964) is a Russian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Russia Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
